(95, 90, 75) 0px 0px 0px 1px, rgba(10, 10, 0, 0.5) 1px 1px 6px 1px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, 黑体, Arial;height: 25px;padding: 8px 0px 5px 5px;text-shadow: rgb(34, 34, 34) 2px 2px 3px;white-space: normal;margin: 18px 0px !important\">X:only-of-type</h3><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13.3333px;line-height: normal;font-family: Arial\">li:only-of-type&nbsp;{&nbsp;font-weight:&nbsp;bold;&nbsp;}</pre><p style=\"margin: 10px auto;font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal\">匹配父元素下使用同种标签的唯一一个子元素，等同于:first-of-type:last-of-type或 :nth-of-type(1):nth-last-of-type(1)</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto;font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal\"><a href=\"http://d2o0t5hpnwv4c1.cloudfront.net/840_cssSelectors/selectors/onlyOfType.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85)\">查看演示</a></p><h5 style=\"font-size: 12px;margin: 10px 0px;font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal\">兼容性</h5><ol style=\"padding-left: 40px;font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>IE9</p></li><li><p>Firefox 3.5+</p></li><li><p>Chrome</p></li><li><p>Safari</p></li><li><p>Opera</p></li></ol><h3 style=\"font-size: 17px;line-height: 25px;background: rgb(43, 102, 149);border-radius: 6px;box-shadow: rgb(95, 90, 75) 0px 0px 0px 1px, rgba(10, 10, 0, 0.5) 1px 1px 6px 1px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, 黑体, Arial;height: 25px;padding: 8px 0px 5px 5px;text-shadow: rgb(34, 34, 34) 2px 2px 3px;white-space: normal;margin: 18px 0px !important\">X:first-of-type</h3><pre style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13.3333px;line-height: normal;font-family: Arial\">li:only-of-type&nbsp;{&nbsp;font-weight:&nbsp;bold;&nbsp;}</pre><p style=\"margin: 10px auto;font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal\">匹配父元素下使用同种标签的第一个子元素，等同于:nth-of-type(1)</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto;font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal\"><a href=\"http://d2o0t5hpnwv4c1.cloudfront.net/840_cssSelectors/selectors/firstOfType.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85)\">查看演示</a></p><h5 style=\"font-size: 12px;margin: 10px 0px;font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal\">兼容性</h5><ol style=\"padding-left: 40px;font-family: 微软雅黑, PTSans, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>IE9</p></li><li><p>Firefox 3.5+</p></li><li><p>Chrome</p></li><li><p>Safari</p></li><li><p>Opera</p></li></ol><p><br/></p>', '沐兮丨丶', '2020-03-11 09:02:31', 666, 4242, 100000, '1', '/uploads/20200311/6835018fc11dc3d1128245abd40c13c2.jpg', 0, NULL);
INSERT INTO `blogs` VALUES (6, 'Vuex 快速入门 简单易懂 ', 24, '1', '1. 借鉴 了Flux、Redux、 The Elm Architecture\n\n2. 专为 Vue.js 设计 的状态管理模式\n\n3. 集中式存储和管理应用程序中所有组件的状态\n\n4. Vuex 也集成到 Vue 的官方调试工具\n\n5. 一个 Vuex 应用的核心是 store（仓库，一个容器），store包含着你的应用中大部分的状态 (state)。', '<h1 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 26px; margin: 22px 0px 16px; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, Sathu, EucrosiaUPC, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.8; padding: 0px; min-height: 1rem; border: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">一、vuex介绍</h1><p><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, Sathu, EucrosiaUPC, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.8; margin: 22px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; font-size: 24px; border: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（1）vuex是什么？</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1. 借鉴&nbsp;了<a href=\"https://facebook.github.io/flux/docs/overview.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); text-decoration-line: none;\">Flux</a>、<a href=\"http://redux.js.org/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); text-decoration-line: none;\">Redux</a>、&nbsp;<a href=\"https://guide.elm-lang.org/architecture/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); text-decoration-line: none;\">The Elm Architecture</a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2. 专为 Vue.js 设计&nbsp;的<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">状态管理模式</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3. 集中式存储和管理应用程序中所有组件的状态</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4. Vuex 也集成到 Vue 的官方调试工具</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">5. 一个 Vuex 应用的核心是 store（仓库，一个容器），store包含着你的应用中大部分的<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">状态 (state)</span>。</p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, Sathu, EucrosiaUPC, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.8; margin: 22px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; font-size: 24px; border: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（2）什么情况下我应该使用 Vuex？</h2><p><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, Sathu, EucrosiaUPC, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.8; margin: 22px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; font-size: 22px; border: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1. 不适用：小型简单应用，用 Vuex 是繁琐冗余的，更适合使用简单的&nbsp;<a href=\"https://cn.vuejs.org/v2/guide/state-management.html#%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E8%B5%B7%E6%AD%A5%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); text-decoration-line: none;\">store 模式</a>。</h3><p><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, Sathu, EucrosiaUPC, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.8; margin: 22px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; font-size: 22px; border: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2. 适用于：中大型单页应用，你可能会考虑如何<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">把组件的共享状态抽取出来，以一个全局单例模式管理，不管在哪个组件，都能获取状态/触发行为</span>，解决问题如下：</h3><p><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><h4 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, Sathu, EucrosiaUPC, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.8; margin: 22px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; border: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">① 多个视图使用于同一状态：</h4><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">传参的方法对于多层嵌套的组件将会非常繁琐，并且对于兄弟组件间的状态传递无能为力</p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><h4 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, Sathu, EucrosiaUPC, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.8; margin: 22px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; border: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">② 不同视图需要变更同一状态：</h4><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">采用父子组件直接引用或者通过事件来变更和同步状态的多份拷贝，通常会导致无法维护的代码</p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, Sathu, EucrosiaUPC, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.8; margin: 22px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; font-size: 24px; border: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（3）Vuex 和单纯的全局对象有何不同？</h2><p><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, Sathu, EucrosiaUPC, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.8; margin: 22px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; font-size: 22px; border: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1.Vuex 的状态存储是响应式的</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当 Vue 组件从 store 中读取状态的时候，若 store 中的状态发生变化，那么相应的组件也会相应地得到高效更新。</p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, Sathu, EucrosiaUPC, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.8; margin: 22px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; font-size: 22px; border: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2.你不能直接改变 store 中的状态</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">改变 store 中的状态的唯一途径就是显式地<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">提交 (commit) mutation</span>，方便我们跟踪每一个状态的变化。</p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><h1 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 26px; margin: 22px 0px 16px; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, Sathu, EucrosiaUPC, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.8; padding: 0px; min-height: 1rem; border: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">二、vuex安装</h1><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">* vue cli 3 中搭建脚手架预设时选择了“vuex”后便安装了vuex，可跳过此步阅读</p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, Sathu, EucrosiaUPC, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.8; margin: 22px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; font-size: 24px; border: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（1）&lt;script&gt;引入</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在 Vue 之后引入&nbsp;<code style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, &quot;Ubuntu Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; margin: 0px 3px; padding: 3px 4px; border: none; border-radius: 4px; background: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">vuex</code>&nbsp;会进行自动安装：</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, &quot;Ubuntu Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: normal; overflow: auto; position: relative; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 1em; border: none; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">&lt;script&nbsp;src=&quot;/path/to/vue.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;script&nbsp;src=&quot;/path/to/vuex.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</pre><p><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, Sathu, EucrosiaUPC, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.8; margin: 22px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; font-size: 24px; border: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（2） 包管理</h2><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, &quot;Ubuntu Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: normal; overflow: auto; position: relative; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 1em; border: none; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.5; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">npm&nbsp;install&nbsp;vuex&nbsp;--save&nbsp;//yarn&nbsp;add&nbsp;vuex</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Micr