INSERT INTO `blogs` VALUES (46, 'PostCSS--css必备', 3, '1', 'PostCSS--css必备\n', '<p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s;\">什么是postcss</strong></p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">postcss 一种对css编译的工具，类似babel对js的处理，常见的功能如:</p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1. 使用下一代css语法</p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2. 自动补全浏览器前缀</p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3. 自动把px代为转换成rem(rem不熟悉的，点这)</p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4. css 代码压缩等等</p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">postcss 只是一个工具，本身不会对css一顿操作，它通过插件实现功能，autoprefixer 就是其一。</p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s;\">与 less sass 的区别</strong></p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">less sass 是预处理器，用来支持扩充css语法。</p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">postcss 既不是 预处理器也不是 后处理器，其功能比较广泛，而且重要的一点是，postcss可以和less/sass结合使用</p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s;\">关于取舍</strong></p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">虽然可以结合less/sass使用，但是它们还是有很多重复功能，用其中一个基本就 ok 了。</p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">以下是个人的总结:</p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">postcss 鼓励开发者使用规范的CSS原生语法编写源代码，支持未来的css语法，就像babel支持ES6。</p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">less、sass 扩展了原生的东西，它把css作为一个子集，但这不好保持向后兼容。</p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">总体来说区别不大，看个人喜好吧</p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s;\">如何使用</strong></p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这里只说在webpack里集成使用，首先需要 loader</p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1. 安装</p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">npm install postcss-loader –save-dev</p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2. webpack配置</p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">一般与其他loader配合使用，下面*标部分才是postcss用到的</p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">配合时注意loader的顺序(从下面开始加载)</p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3. postcss配置</p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">项目根目录新建 postcss.config.js文件，里面配置一些插件</p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">注:也可以在webpack中配置</p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s;\">常用的postcss插件</strong></p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s;\">1. Autoprefixer</strong></p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">前缀补全，全自动的，无需多说</p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">安装:</p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">cnpm install Autoprefixer --save-dev</p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s;\">2. postcss-cssnext</strong></p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">使用下个版本的css语法【关于语法另一篇文章会单独讲】</p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">安装:</p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">cnpm install postcss-cssnext --save-dev</p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s;\">3. postcss-pxtorem</strong></p><p style=\"transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; ma