5.96px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><p class=\"f-ust f-ust-1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 4px; padding: 0px; outline: none; user-select: text; cursor: text; line-height: 18px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">フリ（ふり）まですると まわりや自分（じぶん）さえ見（み）えなくなってしまうから</p><p class=\"f-ust f-ust-1 f-fs0 translated\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 4px; padding: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 12px; user-select: text; cursor: text; line-height: 18px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">再这样装模作样下去的话 不管是周围的人还是自己 都会看不清的</p></div><div class=\"j-line trans\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7); font-family: arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Mongolian Baiti&quot;; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 15.96px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><p class=\"f-ust f-ust-1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 4px; padding: 0px; outline: none; user-select: text; cursor: text; line-height: 18px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">辿（たど）り着（つ）いた先（さき） 見（み）つけられたもの 譲（ゆず）れないものはあるんですか</p><p class=\"f-ust f-ust-1 f-fs0 translated\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 4px; padding: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 12px; user-select: text; cursor: text; line-height: 18px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">在到达的前方 发现了 原来也有绝不拱手让出的东西的呢</p></div><div class=\"j-line trans\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7); font-family: arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Mongolian Baiti&quot;; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 15.96px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><p class=\"f-ust f-ust-1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 4px; padding: 0px; outline: none; user-select: text; cursor: text; line-height: 18px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">振（ふ）り返（か）ればすぐ そこにある帰（かえ）る場所（ばしょ）</p><p class=\"f-ust f-ust-1 f-fs0 translated\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 4px; padding: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 12px; user-select: text; cursor: text; line-height: 18px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">回过头来的话 马上 就能找到能回去的地方</p></div><div class=\"j-line trans\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7); font-family: arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Mongolian Baiti&quot;; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 15.96px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><p class=\"f-ust f-ust-1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 4px; padding: 0px; outline: none; user-select: text; cursor: text; line-height: 18px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">不透明（ふとうめい）な世（よ）の中（なか）で</p><p class=\"f-ust f-ust-1 f-fs0 translated\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 4px; padding: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 12px; user-select: text; cursor: text; line-height: 18px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">在不透明的这个世界中</p></div><div class=\"j-line trans\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7); font-family: arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Mongolian Baiti&quot;; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 15.96px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><p class=\"f-ust f-ust-1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 4px; padding: 0px; outline: none; user-select: text; cursor: text; line-height: 18px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">不安（ふあん）で</p><p class=\"f-ust f-ust-1 f-fs0 translated\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 4px; padding: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 12px; user-select: text; cursor: text; line-height: 18px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">不安着</p></div><div class=\"j-line trans\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7); font-family: arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Mongolian Baiti&quot;; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 15.96px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><p class=\"f-ust f-ust-1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 4px; padding: 0px; outline: none; user-select: text; cursor: text; line-height: 18px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">私（わたし）に大（おお）きな事（こと）は出来（でき）ないよ</p><p class=\"f-ust f-ust-1 f-fs0 translated\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 4px; padding: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 12px; user-select: text; cursor: text; line-height: 18px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">我呀 也做不成什么了不起的事情呢</p></div><div class=\"j-line trans\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7); font-family: arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Mongolian Baiti&quot;; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 15.96px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><p class=\"f-ust f-ust-1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 4px; padding: 0px; outline: none; user-select: text; cursor: text; line-height: 18px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">だけど 側（そば）にいる</p><p class=\"f-ust f-ust-1 f-fs0 translated\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 4px; padding: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 12px; user-select: text; cursor: text; line-height: 18px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">能在你身边就够了</p></div><div class=\"j-line trans\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7); font-family: arial, sans-serif, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Mongolian Baiti&quot;; font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 15.96px; white-space: normal; background-color: r